            "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
            "body": "This is my point: if you set `CYTHON_LIMITED_API` (from the outside), it has no effect because of the `&& 0` at the end of the directive.\r\n\r\nPeople may think \"oh, I can try setting `CYTHON_LIMITED_API` to get me closer to `Py_LIMITED_API`\", but actually it doesn't do that at all (in its current form).\r\n",
